create two private subnets (10.0.3.0/24, 10.0.4.0/24) with access to the internet through nat instance
      = create nat instance with ami (amazon linux 2023) and user data to install and configure iptables to run as nat instance ( make sure to auto assing public IP )
      = make sure that it's security group should allow inbound port (80,443) from (10.0.0.0/16) (vpc cidr block)
      = disalbe source/distination checks
      =  create route table with rule that routes 0.0.0.0/0(internet) to the nat instance
      = associate this route table to the two private subnets created earlier
